<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.4">
<l>ētavaṉ tolpiṟappi ḷaiyavaṉvaḷai yūtimaṉṉar</l>
<l>tūtuva ṉāyavaṉūr colvīrkaḷcol   līraṟiyēṉ</l>
<l>mātavaṉ taṉṟuṇaiyā naṭantāḷtaṭañ cūḻpuṟavil</l>
<l>pōtuvaṇ ṭāṭucemmal puṉalālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is his ancestral lineage? You who [can] say the city of that young man,</l>
<l>The one who became a messenger for the kings, blowing [his] conch, tell me!</l>
<l>I don’t know! She behaved as Mādhava’s companion.</l>
<l rend="indent">Are they setting out for Āli</l>
<l>With abundant waters where bees dance on buds</l>
<l rend="indent">in the woodlands encircled by ponds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
